DOC.brief_summary: The purpose of this study is to Demonstrate the Relative Bioavailability of Cefzil 250 mg/5 ml Cefprozil Oral Suspension Following a 10 ml Dose Fasting Conditions.
DOC.brief_title: To Demonstrate the Relative Bioavailability of Cefzil 250 mg/5 ml Cefprozil Oral Suspension Following a 10 ml Dose Fasting Conditions.
DOC.criteria: No clinically significant abnormal finding on physical exam, medical history, or clinical laboratory results on screening. Positive test results for HIV or hepatitis B or C. Treatment for drug or alcohol dependence.
